    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term formerly referring to a bivalve shell-fish such as the mussel or oyster; in more recent usage, refers to any large marine snail with a spiraling shell that is pointed on both ends.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
